trailingComments.value:
*
 * Load a FZP file from the given URL.
 *
 * @example
 * const {FZPUtils} = require('fzp-js')
 *
 * FZPUtils.loadFZP('core/Arduino Nano3(fix).fzp')
 * .then((fzz) => {
 *   console.log(fzz.fz)
 * })
 * .catch((err) => {
 *   console.error(err)
 * })
 *
 * @param {String} src
 * @param {String} url URL to the FZP file.
 * @return {Promise}
